title: Stock futures slip in Asia amid trade standoff
text: Stock futures turned red in Asia early on Monday as a standoff in Sino-U.S. trade talks blunted risk appetite, underpinning safe harbors including the Japanese yen and sovereign bonds.

title: The Week In Cannabis: A&F Tries CBD, GW Pharma Soars On Results, Denver Decriminalizes Mushrooms
text: The cannabis world had an unlikely protagonist: magic mushrooms. After a popular vote, the city of Denver, Colorado, known as a legal cannabis trailblazer, approved a ballot measure to decriminalize psychedelic mushrooms at its active ingredient, psilocybin.
